data_table.name: f30_rel2
data_table.description: Form 30 - Medical History Questionnaire -- hospitalization history; history of medical conditions; history of heart, circulatory, or coagulation problems; history of arthritis, gallbladder disease, thyroid disease, hypertension, angina, peripheral arterial disease and related procedures, colonoscopy or sigmoidoscopy, stool guaiac; history of cancers (site, age at diagnosis); recent history of falls or syncopal episodes; history of fractures (site, age, number). This self-administered questionnaire was required for all OS participants.
